            "title": "特朗普與委內瑞拉代總統在「非常好的通話」中就石油、貿易問題進行討論",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普與委內瑞拉代總統在「非常好的通話」中就石油、貿易問題進行討論\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XKJLRnWCVcH78s76CgLfFg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/b9998e50-f1ad-11f0-b5b3-55be6a11f707\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普與委內瑞拉代總統在「非常好的通話」中就石油、貿易問題進行討論</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
